title: Power Burkas "Holes" - Converse Make Noise Barcelona
description:
Spanish up-and-comers Power Burka were handpicked to support Wavves at our Make Noise gig at Sala Apolo, Barcelona.

Converse Make Noise is a celebration of undiscovered music talent in Spain. 

Track "Holes" by Power Burkas
